title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Lavelle/Stump The Snob: Music Edition/Baratz/Krawczynski/Birk
description: Nordo is in again for PA and is joined by freshly awake Lavelle E. Neal III. A musical edition of Stump the Snob with Chris Hawkey, Cory Cove and Producer Brianne. Sports agent and president of Team IFA, Blake Baratz joins. Jonny Athletic calls in from the lake on a well deserved break. And Matt Birk in studio!
